      "code": "# Search for verses containing pieces like \"ولقد ارسلنا\" and \"من قبلك\"\ncands=[]\nfor v in quran:\n    t=v['ayah_text']\n    n=norm(t)\n    if 'ولقد ارسلنا' in n and 'من قبلك' in n:\n        cands.append((v['surah_name'], v['ayah_id'], t))\nlen(cands), cands[:10]",
